data.description: This NICELY CARED FOR HOME, provides 2 BEDS/2 BATHS + a cozy DEN + and a spacious screened LANAI with a beautiful tiled, IN-GROUND SPA. Some of the nice features you will appreciate include:  lovely Bahama Shutters, the convenient INTERIOR LAUNDRY Closet, the EXTRA GARAGE REFRIGERATOR, and plenty of SORAGE CABINETS, 5 CEILING FANS, and the DISAPPEARING LANAI POCKET SLIDER DOOR to expand your living to the outdoors.  There is an abundance of space in the Living Rm and the MA Bedrm, and the Den sliding pocket doors add versatility and privacy.  The NEW ROOF, NEW AC SYSTEM AND NEW SPA PUMP, will give you worry free, peace of mind in your New Home.  There is even a full house Surround Sound for your enjoyment of your favorite music. This is a more quiet, and less busy LOCATION in the community, away from the front entrance, with easy access to the Country Club and Gulf Course.  Just around the corner is the Waterfront with Dining at Cass Cay, the Trading Post / Ship Store, Boat Storage and Launch.  There's plenty of OPTIONAL Amenities for your enjoyment- all with separate fees. These original owners leave behind a warm and peaceful ambience of their many happy years here. Welcome Home!
